Ain't America Grand,<br><br>
Makes you wonder why someone wouldn't fight for it.  Baby boys don't know what crap is.  <br><br>
They should all stand time in a SEER training camp or advanced survival.  A little time in the POW training camp (bet they didn't know about those), I really enjoyed that experience as well as parachuting into the ocean in a squall just to see if I could handle the experience.  Throw in a little snake school.<br><br>
Not even close to the real thing and we lost three guys in stress training.<br><br>
By the way.  Know where they sent me after over three years in SEA.  1 year isolated tour DEW Line Artic to cool off.  The solitude did great things and damn it was quiet.  Used to walk solo out on the ice.  Didn't much give a shit.My ears still ring loud as hell.<br><br>
Ed you are right.  Home is great.  Shit I thought a candy bar and a coke was heaven.  Used to dream about the stuff everyone else takes for granted.
